seo: 言中摄像头,默认口令漏洞,高危,摄像头安全,漏洞检测
seo_en: Yanzhong Camera,default credential vulnerability,high severity,camera security,vulnerability detection
summary: 该插件旨在检测言中摄像头是否存在默认用户名和密码（admin/admin）的漏洞，并提取设备厂商、产品型号和固件版本信息。
summary_en: This plugin is designed to detect whether the Yanzhong camera has the default username and password (admin/admin) vulnerability, and extract the device manufacturer, product model, and firmware version information.
